steps for Oauth:
1.generate code,client id,client secret.

2.
:POST
https://accounts.zoho.com/oauth/v2/token?code=1000.d0e80492f1301365726ca0d03e6e76e8.d2773e366de8ae4fb582c9134d3851df&grant_type=authorization_code&client_id=1000.J0XRRSHZPAINZS1ANJZWB8GH0WQHDV&client_secret=03bc0e927b05db03b3a16f576cce461d5944678e3a

:RESPONSE
{
    "access_token": "1000.c94a153300e4183ddc2742ab5b4c4716.28beb176c9ab98ef8b73bbe94cf3cb3c",
    "refresh_token": "1000.db4a96a4cde562ece5d095ff0f4d639a.47e6c8e78df14e558b6dac40c2e41111",
    "api_domain": "https://www.zohoapis.com",
    "token_type": "Bearer",
    "expires_in": 3600
}
3.Access API
:GET
-H orgId VALUE => 736760434
-H Authorization  VALUE => Zoho-oauthtoken 1000.df76e8cf11d879b40060687818d04a2a.3e1e0d341ab3cf9e238c632fbf6cdbfe
https://desk.zoho.com/api/v1/tickets?include=contacts,assignee,departments,team,isRead

4.refresh token
https://accounts.zoho.com/oauth/v2/token?refresh_token=1000.db4a96a4cde562ece5d095ff0f4d639a.47e6c8e78df14e558b6dac40c2e41111&client_id=1000.J0XRRSHZPAINZS1ANJZWB8GH0WQHDV&client_secret=03bc0e927b05db03b3a16f576cce461d5944678e3a&grant_type=refresh_token&scope=Desk.tickets.ALL

:RESPONSE
{
    "access_token": "1000.df76e8cf11d879b40060687818d04a2a.3e1e0d341ab3cf9e238c632fbf6cdbfe",
    "api_domain": "https://www.zohoapis.com",
    "token_type": "Bearer",
    "expires_in": 3600
}
